{"id":27993,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/27993","type":2,"name":"BLUE DRAGON","name_cn":"蓝龙","summary":"    在遥远的过去，有着光与黑暗的战斗。然后在那场战斗中，有七位叫作光之战士的人们以他们的力量封印了黑暗而结束战争。那个故事最后也成为神话，他们所持的影之力也被他们的后裔秘密地继承著。\r\n    然后有位戈鲁昂帝国之王，奈那发现自己的影之力，为了征服世界，而展开杀戮和破坏。而同样拥有影之力的左拉为了阻止他的野心，于是与七名光之战士的末裔吉罗一起找寻剩下的末裔。\r\n    在塔塔村中则有着两位每天过著和平日子，希望成为骑士王的修和青梅竹马克露克。他们所住的地方也遭到鲁昂帝国的攻击。在战斗当中，修的影兽“蓝龙”也逐渐苏醒过来。\r\n    于是为了打倒奈那，然后也为了不要再让悲伤被扩大，修他们决定与左拉一行人一起行动进行冒险。","eps":[{"id":133808,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133808","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":2,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133809,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133809","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133810,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133810","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133811,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133811","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133812,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133812","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133813,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133813","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133814,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133814","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133815,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133815","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133816,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133816","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133817,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133817","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":133818,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/133818","type":0,"